        <updateDate>2020-11-04T13:30:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill allows a medical expense tax deduction for face masks, surface disinfectants, and hand sanitizers during the period of the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency beginning on the enactment of this bill and ending when the COVID-19 emergency period has terminated. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
